# Rule: Module Stub Consistency

## Description
All backend modules (e.g., `llm/`, `memory/`, `orchestration/`) must follow consistent stubbing patterns for rapid onboarding and tool-based agent development.

## Requirements
- Top-of-file purpose comment
- `# filepath:` comment
- Placeholder imports
- Class/function declarations matching `masterplan.md`
- `# TODO:` markers

## Scope
Applies to: `agents`, `llm`, `memory`, `integrations`, `orchestration`

